### 获取菜单列表
GET http://{{domain}}/admin/auth/rule/index
Batoken: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

### 添加菜单
POST http://{{domain}}/admin/auth/rule/add
Batoken: {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "New Menu",
